OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Conservative Party co-chair Ben Elliott
OL,6, has been warned to maintain a "clear   
OL,7, distinction" between his public duties 
OL,8, and his private business interests.    
OL,10,FThe lobbying watchdog investigated     
OL,11,Fafter reports suggested Mr Elliott's   
OL,12,Ffirm Quintessentially had arranged     
OL,13,Faccess to top politicians for clients. 
OL,15,FIt found it "had not been engaging in  
OL,16,Fconsultant lobbying activity".         
OL,18,FBut it urged Mr Elliott to be          
OL,19,F"cautious" and ensure his two roles    
OL,20,Fremain separate.                       
